videos.headline: Texas burns Kansas for 75-yard TD on first play from scrimmage
videos.description: Shane Buechele finds Jacorey Warrick, who speeds into the end zone for a 75-yard score on the Longhorns' first play from scrimmage.

videos.headline: Kansas stuns Texas with winning FG in OT
videos.description: For the first time since 1938, Kansas shocks Texas when Matthew Wyman drills the winning 25-yard field goal in overtime.
